data.description: Discover the perfect blend of modern comfort and timeless charm at 41 Suzanne Dr, Angier NC. This updated 4-bedroom home, complete with office and den spaces, offers 3.5 baths for a complete living set up.  As you enter, be welcomed by the warmth of Luxury Vinyl Tile flooring installed in 2021. The kitchen features quartz countertops installed in 2022 for a perfect blend of style and functionality.  Recent upgrades bring peace of mind, including a new roof, all new windows in 2020 and hot water heater in 2018.  Sitting on a spacious .58-acre lot, the property provides ample outdoor space for leisure. Enjoy a sense of community at Amary Meadows with low HOA fees.  This home is just 10 minutes from downtown Angier and a mere 9 minutes to I-40. As a bonus, the kitchen refrigerator and the upstairs den TV convey with the property, simplifying your move-in process.
